Subject: Re: [T2] electric vacuum pump

You could get an electric or mechanical vacuum pump off of a diesel 
engine in the junkyard, or you could just go the simple route and tap 
your manifolds.  I would do all four - I've seen it plumbed to just one 
but that always made me uncomfortable.

-David

